                            <p class="card-text text-muted text-justify text-center text-wrap font-weight-bold">The vision of <b>Shakti Education and Welfare Society</b> is to create equal and peaceful society
                            where everybody shares and care for the illiteracy in the society. Poor, exploited and
                            unprivileged people should have equal literacy rate and have the equal opportunity.</p>
