            <h2>About Our Organisation</h2><br>
            <p>United we win , divided we fall . 
            Shakti education and welfare society not only to teach the children basic education to slum,
            underprivileged but to teach them to dream. Learning English, learning to read and write
            would be impossible for those who are underprivileged.
            Just a chance in life, that’s what the children need just a chance. For the piece of meal at a
            restaurant you can save a child from a life of begging, rag picking and worst still from crime
            and prostitution.
            With no food, no hope and no family there is no hope for these children.
            Without the regular monthly support shakti education and welfare society is unable to take
            a new children or continue their ground level work in slums and on the street. Please help to
            give these children elementary education, change for a life , give them hope and future.
            </p>
            <a href="/about" class=" btn card-btn btn-sm">Read More</a>
        </div>
